<i>noun</i>: 부연 [부ː연], 공력 [공녁] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부연 [부ː연]</dt><br>
<dd>expatiation; elaboration</dd><br>
<dd>알기 쉽게 다른 내용을 더하여 자세히 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of adding details to an explanation for easy understanding.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공력 [공녁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. elaboration</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 이루려고 온 마음을 다해 들이는 힘과 정성.</dd><br>
<dd>A strenuous effort sincerely made to achieve certain objectives with wholeheartedness .</dd><br>
<dd>2. Buddhist merit</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서 부처의 가르침대로 선행과 수행을 쌓아서 얻은 힘.</dd><br>
<dd>A form of power acquired by exercising discipline and good deeds by following the teachings of Buddha in Buddhism.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>